---
title: Pesto and Courgette Soup with goat's cheese and crispy croutons
description: What at first may seem like a simple soup becomes something altogether more decadent when you consider its components. Brioche croutons, a goat's cheese crumble and spoonfuls of rich and flavourful pesto are just some of the reasons you're going to love this dish.
